270.en_source: But may I make a suggestion?

272.en_source: It's about your hair, that's why I ask.
272.sl_trans: Gre za vaše lase, zato sprašujem.

274.en_source: I mean, you don't like it?

276.en_source: You're too alive for a perm.
276.sl_trans: Preveč ste živi za trajno zastaranje.

278.en_source: You should pull your hair back.
278.sl_trans: Morali bi si lase potegniti nazaj.

279.sl_source: Storite to, boste videli kaj se bo zgodilo.
279.en_source: Do it and See what happens.
279.sl_trans: Naredite to in poglejte, kaj se bo zgodilo.

280.sl_source: Želite, da dvignem lase, tukaj, sedaj?
280.en_source: Right now, here, you want me to pull my hair back?
280.sl_trans: Zdaj, tukaj, hočeš, da si lase potegnem nazaj?

282.sl_source: To bi raje storil jaz, ampak vsi ti v tej sobi ki se pretvarjajo da naju ne gledajo bi seveda domnevali, da seksava, ali kaj podobnega.
282.en_source: I'd love to do it, but if I did everyone in this room who's pretending not to be watching us would naturally assume we were fucking or something.
282.sl_trans: Z veseljem bi to storil, toda če bi to storil, bi vsi v tej sobi, ki se pretvarjajo, da naju ne gledajo, seveda sklepali, da se jebeva ali kaj podobnega.

289.sl_source: Ženska ramena so prva linija njenih skrivnosti.
289.en_source: A woman's shoulders are the frontlines of her mystique.
289.sl_trans: Ženska ramena so prvi del njene mističnosti.

290.sl_source: Nikogršnja zemlja v boju razuma in telesa.
290.en_source: A no man's land in that battle between the mind and the body.
290.sl_trans: Nikogaršnja zemlja v boju med umom in telesom.

291.sl_source: Z naravno barvo las bi vaše oči prišle do izraza.
291.en_source: You know your natural color would really bring out your eyes.
291.sl_trans: Veste, da bi vaša naravna barva resnično poudarila vaše oči.

294.sl_source: Je pogled iz tvojega balkona tudi takšen?
294.en_source: From your terrace, do you have this view?
294.sl_trans: Ali imate s svoje terase takšen razgled?

296.sl_source: Nimam balkona in sem približno dvanajst nadstropij niže.
296.en_source: No terrace and I'm about 12 floors down.
296.sl_trans: Brez terase in približno 12 nadstropij nižje.
